originalText.text: Dr. Kane is so great!  He has a great bedside manner and really took the time to listen to me.  He is truly reliable and demonstrates highly skilled medical knowledge.  I am so happy I found him to help manage my pain. Would highly recommend!

originalText.text: Dr. Kane is a wonderful and kind osteopath. Having suffered with a plethora of musculoskeletal issues, I was seeking a provider who had a non-traditional approach and understood my body as a whole. Dr. Kane took the time to listen and evaluate my concerns. He came up with a treatment plan that suited my needs and relieved pain that I had been experiencing for years. If you are looking for a provider with a kind heart and who thinks outside the box, I would recommend Dr. Kane.

originalText.text: Luke is an exceptional physician. He is highly skilled at ultrasonography and musculoskeletal medicine. He is dedicated to his patients, offers them many options. Luke has performed evaluations of my knee joints and offered diagnostic information from the scan alone. I would see Luke to see what my options are before I considered treatment for my aches and pains.
